      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking great value and dependable transportation. It's the perfect opportunity to own a capable car at an accessible price point!",
