    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project with this budget-friendly find! While this vehicle has seen better days and will need some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast looking for a base to build upon. It's being sold as-is, making it an affordable entry point for someone ready to put in the work and bring it back to life!",
